oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This Photograph Gives an Overview of the Campus of the Tennessee Agricultural and Industrial State Normal School in 1916. Pictured are (1) Main or Academic Building, (2)Wilsonian Hall, a Dormitory For Women, and (3) Men's Hall, the Dormitory For Men. All Were Built in 1912.
